"snippet" : "Name Description Assert_WString_Equal(THIS^, <actual>, <reference>, \"\") Successful when the actual value matches the reference value. Assert_WString_NotEqual(THIS^, <actual>, <reference>, \"\") Successful when the actual value does not match the reference value. Assert_WString_Contains(THIS^, <actual>...", 
