"snippet" : "Edit Comment Function : The command opens the Comment dialog for adding a comment to a test step, test case, or test case group. Call : Test Table menu; context menu in the tabular editor Requirement : A test step, test case, or test case group is selected. Dialog: Comment Comment The comment given ...", 
